1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
A chatbot answers questions.
An AI Partner does a job.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:10,000
This Partner has a written role: what it reads,
what it produces, what it may never do.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:16,000
I drop in a meeting note —
it drafts the tracker and the report.

4
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Then it stops. Nothing gets sent.
Everything waits in a drafts folder for a human.

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:26,000
That rule is permanent.

6
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:36,000
That's an AI Partner.
The full 90-second demo is on the channel.
